1
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:43,640
Xu Qingqing

2
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,000
is dead.

3
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:08,479
What happened?

4
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:16,360
Life is unpredictable.

5
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:19,759
A person can die just like that.

6
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,000
Did you do this?

7
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,719
If I were to kill someone,

8
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,159
why would I go to such trouble?

9
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:32,400
It's poison.

10
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:34,919
Her face is pale,

11
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,879
and she is bleeding from her mouth, eyes, and ears.

12
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:40,039
She must have been poisoned.

13
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:41,639
What did she eat before she died?

14
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:50,199
Who was present when she died?

15
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:52,840
I was.

16
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,240
Last night, in the Hour of the Ox,

17
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,159
the Eunuch asked me to prepare some late-night snacks.

18
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:09,240
Eunuch,

19
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:12,759
I prepared some food as you ordered.

20
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,759
Eunuch,

21
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:00,479
I prepared some for her as well.

22
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:03,759
Should I give it to her?

23
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:06,639
Feed her some.

24
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,800
If she starves to death, we won't learn anything.

25
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,040
Eat something.

26
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:23,240
But I didn't kill her.

27
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:26,879
All the food was checked by the Secret Inspectorate.

28
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:27,680
There was no poison.

29
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:41,079
This scent...

30
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,279
Could it be...

31
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,720
to avenge the Villa Master, she...

32
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,560
so...

33
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:48,879
Young Master Ye,

34
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:53,439
someone has been killed right in front of me.

35
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:56,959
If you don't give me a satisfactory answer,

36
00:04:59,399 --> 00:05:01,439
for my own protection,

37
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,959
I will have no choice.

38
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,160
Eunuch, please rest assured.

39
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,800
I will keep my word.

40
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,920
But before dusk, no one dies.

41
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,120
Young Master Ye,

42
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,040
please.

43
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:29,079
Let's go.

44
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,480
Lady Si,

45
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,279
no need to follow for now.

46
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,160
Take me with you.

47
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,519
Let me go with you.

48
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,519
Ye Li has already solved the third line.

49
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:10,879
This Young Master Ye is indeed interesting.

50
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:14,759
No wonder he gives Lord Nine Thousand Years a headache.

51
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,000
Your Highness,

52
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:24,399
the letters are all here.

53
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,959
It seems your subordinate and Ye Li

54
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,759
work quite well together.

55
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,399
It is Your Highness who has great foresight.

56
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:34,160
The Secret Inspectorate has arrived.

57
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,439
I want to catch them all at once.

58
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:38,920
I need Lord Yin to select a squad of Dali Temple elites

59
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:40,439
to stand by.

60
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:42,920
Yes.

61
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,839
Crown Prince,

62
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,399
our spy within the Secret Inspectorate

63
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,639
has already transferred some antidote pills to us.

64
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,360
Xiao Bai and I went to the Lotus Garden again this morning.

65
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,160
Look.

66
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,040
Isn't this a dragon?

67
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:21,160
So the "Water Immortal"...

68
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,160
refers neither to the narcissus nor the lotus.

69
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,240
It's a dragon.

70
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:28,319
After the heavy rain,

71
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,600
water accumulated in the vat,

72
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:32,319
and a dragon pattern appeared on the lotus leaves.

73
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:34,160
And this dragon pattern...

74
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:36,560
is exactly the same as the one here in the Main Hall.

75
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,560
That's not right.

76
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:40,879
Look here.

77
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,439
This statue is the famous Fire God, Zhurong.

78
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:45,720
One of the Five Element Gods of Taoism.

79
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,480
He is supposed to be...

80
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:49,160
stepping on two dragons,

81
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:50,759
not a two-headed dragon.

82
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,480
The two-headed dragon pattern in the lotus leaves...

83
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:54,920
refers to this very spot.

84
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:58,720
If the Villa Master worships the Fire God,

85
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,720
why not build a statue to worship,

86
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,160
but instead only made this screen?

87
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:05,800
"The Immortal points the way to the Book of Longevity."

88
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,680
Could it be that the Villa Master...

89
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:10,519
is seeking immortality through alchemy?

90
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:11,959
No.

91
00:08:11,959 --> 00:08:13,879
The Fire God isn't in charge of longevity.

92
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,839
Lend me your map for a look.

93
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,800
W-What map?

94
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:21,560
The map of the villa you secretly drew.

95
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:23,000
Don't try to trick me.

96
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:23,879
Who, who, who...

97
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,120
I saw it that day.

98
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,319
Fine, here, take it.

99
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,480
Coming all this way,

100
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:32,759
not only did I fail to swipe anything,

101
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,840
but I also lost quite a bit.

102
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:38,600
Look.

103
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,159
Wanxiang Pavilion,

104
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,559
Lotus Garden,

105
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:43,480
Main Hall.

106
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:47,559
These three places are located in the due west,

107
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:49,279
due north, and due east of the villa.

108
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:52,480
Don't you think...

109
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,519
this is all too coincidental?

110
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:56,240
Yes.

111
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:57,919
On this map,

112
00:08:58,279 --> 00:08:59,519
the only place we haven't been is due south.

113
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,000
What is this place?

114
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,919
Across the Chi River is the Ancestral Hall.

115
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,559
The Ancestral Hall.

116
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:16,279
Greetings, Imperial Grandmother.

117
00:09:16,279 --> 00:09:16,840
Greetings, Empress Dowager.

118
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:18,480
Rise.

119
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,639
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

120
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,759
Thank you, Imperial Grandmother.

121
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:26,399
Baixiao Villa...

122
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:27,879
what kind of place is it exactly?

123
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,360
Why does everyone want to go there?

124
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,559
Answering Imperial Grandmother:

125
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,799
I heard that Baixiao Villa...

126
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,559
holds a Thousand Mechanism Secret Treasure,

127
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,360
which has been linked to multiple deaths.

128
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,519
I feared more disasters would arise,

129
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,840
so I sent the Dali Temple Justice,

130
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,960
Hua Qiankun, to go there with Ye Li.

131
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,679
Who is Ye Li?

132
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:47,200
Ye Li is the son of the former Vice Minister of Revenue, Ye Zhongming.

133
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,960
Because he was implicated in the murder of the Capital Governor,

134
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:51,600
he went to the villa to atone for his crimes through service.

135
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,279
And what about you, Eunuch Li?

136
00:09:53,279 --> 00:09:56,320
This old servant also wishes to share the burdens of the Empress Dowager and His Majesty.

137
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:58,000
Fearing the Thousand Mechanism Secret Treasure...

138
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,559
might be used by those with ill intent,

139
00:09:59,919 --> 00:10:02,759
I sent the Secret Inspectorate to investigate.

140
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,799
Don't think I don't know what you are thinking.

141
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,320
His Majesty is critically ill,

142
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,759
but I am not dead yet.

143
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:11,720
You seem rather impatient.

144
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:13,679
This old servant dares not.

145
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:14,399
Your grandson dares not.

146
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,639
With His Majesty bedridden,

147
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,200
we must not fall into chaos.

148
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,639
If there is any progress in this case,

149
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,240
report to me first.

150
00:10:24,639 --> 00:10:25,399
Yes.
